Package: librdkit1t64
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: RDKit runtime libraries and data files
 RDKit is a cheminformatics and machine-learning toolkit.
 .
 This package ships the runtime shared libraries and data files required by
 the PostgreSQL cartridge build used by Pigsty.

Package: postgresql-@PG_MAJOR@-rdkit
Section: database
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, postgresql-@PG_MAJOR@, librdkit1t64 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: RDKit cartridge for PostgreSQL @PG_MAJOR@
 RDKit adds cheminformatics data types, operators, and functions to
 PostgreSQL.
 .
 This package contains the PostgreSQL @PG_MAJOR@ cartridge with InChI support
 enabled on Debian 13.
